<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Repo Cleaner</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="images/favicon.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/knockout/3.4.2/knockout-min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/actions/index-onload.js"></script>
    <script src="js/ajax/get-ajax.js"></script>
    <script src="js/model/repo-host-model.js"></script>
    <script src="js/model/repo-model.js"></script>
    <script src="js/model/user-model.js"></script>
    <script src="js/viewmodel/index-view-model.js"></script>
</head>
<body onload="indexOnLoad()">
<div>
    <div>
        <button id="login" class="btn btn-primary" type="button">Log In</button>
        <button id="signup" class="btn btn-secondary" type="button">Sign Up</button>
    </div>

    <span>Try it free</span>

    <span>To generate an access token, go to</span>
    <span>https://github.com/settings/tokens/new</span>
    <span>To function correctly, RepoCleaner will need 2 scopes: "repo" and "admin:repo_hook"</span>
    <span>"repo" allows it to create branches, commit to them and raise pull requests</span>
    <span>"admin:repo_hook" allows it to be notified when you accept or reject a pull request</span>
    <span>Note that this is your personal token and functions like a password, so RepoCleaner's changes will appear to be from your account</span>
    <span>The access token can be deleted at any time by going to</span>
    <span>https://github.com/settings/tokens</span>


    <span>Repo Host</span>
    <div data-bind="foreach: repoHosts">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-bind="text: name, click: $root.setRepoHost"></button>
    </div>

    <span id="accountText" data-bind="text: enterAccountNameText"></span>
    <div class="input-group mb-3">
        <div class="input-group-prepend">
            <span id="basic-addon3" class="input-group-text" data-bind="text: repoHostUrlRoot"></span>
        </div>
        <input id="basic-url" type="text" class="form-control" aria-describedby="basic-addon3" data-bind="textInput: user, style: { 'background-color':  validityColor }">
    </div>

    <button id="tryit" class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-bind="click: tryit">Try it!</button>

    <span>Filter</span>

    <span>Repositories</span>
    <div class="input-group mb-3">
        <div class="input-group-prepend">
            <span id="reposRegex-addon" class="input-group-text">Repositories regex</span>
        </div>
        <input id="reposRegex" type="text" class="form-control" aria-describedby="reposRegex-addon" data-bind="textInput: repoRegexLiteral">
    </div>
    <!--<div class="input-group mb-3">-->
        <!--<div class="input-group-prepend">-->
            <!--<span id="branchesRegex-addon" class="input-group-text">Branches regex</span>-->
        <!--</div>-->
        <!--<input id="branchesRegex" type="text" class="form-control" aria-describedby="branchesRegex-addon" data-bind="textInput: branchRegexLiteral">-->
    <!--</div>-->
    <div data-bind="foreach: repos">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-bind="text: name, style: { 'opacity': opacity }"></button>
        <!--<div data-bind="foreach: branches">-->
            <!--<button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" data-bind="text: name, style: { 'opacity': opacity }"></button>-->
        <!--</div>-->
    </div>

    <button id="createAccount" class="btn btn-primary" type="button">Create an account for more options</button>
</div>

</body>
</html>
